About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Gadar 2 Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Gadar 2 Movie Review By Deeksha Sharma. Gadar 2 Featuring Sunny Deol & Ameesha Patel Directed by Anil Sharma is the Most Anticipated Sequel to 2001 Gadar which redefined Mass Cinema in Bollywood, Tara Singh is back for a New Adventure but with same Enemy & his family on the line- Will he make it or break it? Gadar 2 Full Movie Story Outline Explained & Positives Negatives would be shared in this Video. Gadar 2 vs Omg 2 - Who is Your Winner in this Super Clash? snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Something Missamma Episode 06 Pre Wedding MCM
Filmymoji releases its new episode of Missamma series where Middle class Madhu will be forced to assist Penta Reddy in chopping someoneâ€™s hand off. Meanwhile Dupesh lands in jammalamadugu and proposes to take a pre-wedding shoot of bulli Guvva and Sravani. The broker introduces the alliance as a Dubai return and Madhu blackmails him for money for not revealing this narrative. Dupesh takes out bride and the groom along with MCM and Komali for the pre-wedding shoot and instead of taking pictures he convinces bulli Guvva to click his pictures with the bride. Watch the full episode to find out the shocking truth which Dupesh reveals about the marriage and whether NaatuGuntala gang finds out about the whereabouts of Madhu.

'Chala Gaya WWE SeğŸ˜¢' Roman Reigns Bloodline Mystery, Jey Uso Quits WWE - WWE Smackdown Highlights

The WWE SmackDown highlights from the 11th of August 2023 showcased a captivating episode filled with intense action and emotional moments. In today's episode of WWE SmackDown, Roman Reigns took center stage, asserting his dominance as Universal Champion. The SmackDown highlights captured Roman Reigns' commanding presence, both in and out of the ring, as he continued to solidify his position at the top of WWE. Amidst the excitement, a shocking turn of events occurred as tensions within the Uso family escalated. Jey Uso's unexpected decision to quit WWE left fans stunned, and his subsequent attack on his brother Jimmy Uso, marked by a brutal superkick, added an emotional layer to the evening. The dynamic between Jey Uso and Roman Reigns was also on display, as their potential clash loomed in the spotlight. The SmackDown highlights provided a glimpse into the intricate storytelling that unfolded during the full show, leaving fans eagerly anticipating the next chapter in this gripping narrative
The match between Asuka and Charlotte Flair opens the event, with Flair posing confidently before the bell. Asuka charges, but Flair stands tall. They engage in a heated battle with counterattacks and signature moves. Flair gains the upper hand with powerful strikes and chops, but Asuka fights back with her fierce kicks. The action intensifies as Flair dominates, even delivering a top-rope maneuver. Asuka stages a comeback and gains control, prompting Damage CTRL â€“ Bayley, Dakota Kai, and WWE Womenâ€™s Champion IYO SKY â€“ to appear at ringside, causing a distraction.
Amid the chaos, Asuka capitalizes and nearly secures a victory, but the match ends in a no contest due to interference. Bayley targets Flair while SKY takes out Asuka with a missile dropkick. The celebration continues as SKY and Bayley proclaim their dominance, further establishing SKY as the new WWE Womenâ€™s Champion.
Later, AJ Styles faces off against Karrion Kross. The hard-hitting encounter sees both competitors trading offense, with Kross showcasing his power and aggression. However, AJ's resilience and athleticism shine through. Despite Scarlett's interference, AJ manages to secure the win with a Styles Clash, leading to a celebration with The O.C.
In another thrilling contest, Rey Mysterio challenges Austin Theory for the WWE United States Championship. Despite Theory's initial ambush on an injured Santos Escobar, the match is rebooked with Rey taking his place. Rey delivers his high-flying moves and counters, ultimately pinning Theory to become the new United States Champion. The LWO, including Santos Escobar, celebrates Rey's victory.
The event concludes with a tense family reunion as Jimmy Uso confronts his brother, Jey Uso, and Universal Champion Roman Reigns. Jimmy reveals that his actions at SummerSlam were motivated by his love for Jey and his fear of Jey becoming corrupted like Reigns. The emotional confrontation highlights the complex dynamics within The Bloodline stable, leaving the audience intrigued about the future of this storyline. Jey Uso superkick Roman Reigns, Solo Sikoa & Jimmy Uso. Jey Uso quits WWE saying I am out of WWE.

snippet.title: Russia launches Luna-25 mission in race to sample moon's south pole
snippet.description:
A Soyuz-2 Fregat rocket carrying a lunar landing craft blasted off on what Russia hopes will be its first successful moon landing mission in nearly 50 years. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube â–º http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

The unmanned Luna-25's mission to the moon that is expected to take about five days and will seek to land near the south pole of the moon, collecting geological samples from the area. snippet.title: Thai Sticky Rice Recipe in Tamil | Sticky Rice with Mango | Dessert Recipes in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make thai sticky rice recipe in tamil. In this recipe I am going to compare making the recipe with thailand sticky rice as well as with our regular rice. The extra gluten in thai rice make is very stretchy and sticky once it is steamed. Sticky rice can be served in both sweet and savory recipes. The texture of the rice pairs well with other contrasting tastes and textures also the steamed rice has a mild sweetness to it.
#stickyricerecipe #mangostickyrice #thairecipe 

Friends, please do try this thai sticky rice recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Episode 3846: Padosi Ne Ki Padosi Ki Madad
--------------------------------------------------------
Inspector Panday chooses to take Popatlal into custody even though no one is prepared to accept that he is a thief. The police constables pick up Popatlal from his house and bring him to the society's compound. Inspector Chaalu Pandey confronts the auto-rickshaw driver to repeat his statement of how he had helped Popatlal in shifting the tomato basket in the office later, Popatlal explains what exactly occurred to everyone. Will Inspector Panday accept his story?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzayâ€™s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 27 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 10th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

snippet.title: Allah De Bandeya | B Praak | Jaani | Aly Goni | Jasmine Bhasin | Arvindr Khaira | Zohrajabeen
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents 'Allah De Bandeya,' the third music video from B Praakâ€™s debut album â€œZoharajabeen.â€ Immerse yourself in the warmth of B Praak's voice, as Jaani's heart-touching lyrics tell a story of being more than a friend or lover, but a comforting home for someone. The music, tenderly composed by Kartik Dev and artfully arranged by Mir Desai, complements the song's emotive resonance.

Starring the captivating duo of Jasmine Bhasin and Aly Goni, the short film, directed by Arvindr Khaira, weaves a visual narrative that illustrates the transformative power of unconditional love. It explores the profound impact such love can have, showing that when you've found "your person," nothing else in the world matters. 

Listen to 'Allah De Bandeya' and all the hits from "Zohrajabeen" - http://www.umgindia.lnk.to/Zohrajabeen

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 28 Teaser - 10th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3845: Nau Do Gyaara
--------------------------------------------------------
When Bhide fails to discover the tomatoes after a frantic search in Gokuldham, he decides to file a police report. After some time has passed, Chalu Pandey arrives at the society to look into the missing tomatoes. Bhide tells the entire story of how he had been protecting the tomatoes all night and how they vanished the instant he returned home. Chalu Pandey deduces from the sequence of events that someone from the Gokuldham had stolen them. The residents of Gokuldham are outraged, but Bhide assures the cop that we don't doubt them. Chalu Pandey's inquiry continues, and this time he suspects the newspaper person. Will Chalu Pandey apprehend the perpetrator?

Show Name â€“ Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast â€“  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3845, 9 Aug 2023

About the show:

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

When Bhide fails to discover the tomatoes after a frantic search in Gokuldham, he decides to file a police report. After some time has passed, Chalu Pandey arrives at the society to look into the missing tomatoes. Bhide tells the entire story of how he had been protecting the tomatoes all night and how they vanished the instant he returned home. Chalu Pandey deduces from the sequence of events that someone from the Gokuldham had stolen them. The residents of Gokuldham are outraged, but Bhide assures the cop that we don't doubt them. Chalu Pandey's inquiry continues, and this time he suspects the newspaper person. Will Chalu Pandey apprehend the perpetrator?
